ul975 Anthropic-Cybersecurity-Skills** (817 skills) — BloodHound, Velociraptor, Falco, Scapy, Kerberoasting, ADCS, DPAPI, K8s RBAC, container security. Supplementary: gaoqiongxie (754 skills). \| · id:Operational Logical status=identity/: intentionally empty (non-leader). operational/: five built (principles, commands, skill-routing, config, tool-requirements). logical/: placeholder (IR/DFIR NIST 800-61 source wanted). · wf=**Detection**: detection-engineering manages SIEM rules alert tuning. Elastic Security MCP handles rule creation, false positive tuning, attack discovery. **Triage**: security-monitoring classifies alerts Incident Commander SEV1-SEV4 matrix. SEV1/SEV2 IR. SEV3/SEV4 case management tuning. **Response**: security-incident-response runs 14-type MITRE-mapped lifecycle. cortex recommends containment operator executes (the inversion). DFRWS forensics. Regulatory notification jurisdiction. **Hunt**: threat-hunting runs hypothesis-driven proactive searches mukul975 collection. Malicious findings IR. Suspicious findings new detection rules. **All lessons warden.** incident, hunt finding, monitoring gap updates warden's risk register. Repeat incidents indicate control failures. **All containment/remediation operator.** cortex holds execute permissions detects, triages, recommends.